{"tid":1587527,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"被指放生潮聯小巴 盧偉聰：執法標準一樣","createTime":"2019-09-22T12:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T13:45:55.000Z","uid":135867,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"89a280df21046814b09744150eb495487c1139f7","tid":1587527,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:22:57.000Z","msg":"早前旺角紅Van發起佔旺行動，因不滿警員向一名違例泊車的同業抄牌，罷駛並堵塞於亞皆老街與上海街交界，期後有市民前往聲援並斥警方對通菜街的潮聯小巴長期違法霸佔馬路視若無睹。警務處處長盧偉聰今回應指，收到交通 阻塞的投訴後會執法，而各區執法標準一樣。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n盧偉聰表示，明白小巴行業有執業困難，除了警員在街上巡邏外，大多數相關執法是有區內居民投訴，而警員就必然要執法。潮聯小巴去年曾入稟要求當局在佔旺區清場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.memehk.com/posts/10548\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.memehk.com%2Fposts%2F10548&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBgi%2F3qgDO6vJfpFVPRJtUZY%3D&h=f71f0849\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.memehk.com/posts/10548</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cdzWK3X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcdzWK3X.jpg&h=0395e7e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27dd0ab7d817560a86942c1daf379e0f6b1d00b9","tid":1587527,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:23:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1fb3148723c7cbe62e85ffdff5ab44e0eefcb6d1","tid":1587527,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:27:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nd1aPw2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnd1aPw2.jpg&h=285a917e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59c257aacdece334b42d9b58b365b063838bdac0","tid":1587527,"uid":6980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:29:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>【All you need to know about Hong Kong Protests 2019】2.0</strong><